%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Which%20Are%20the%20Companies%20Which%20Donated%20the%20Most%20to%20BJP%20Through%20Electoral%20Bonds%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22084733%2FGJCLQayb0AA6lrb-e1711077496883.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20which%20secured%20approximately%20half%20of%20all%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20received%20the%20highest%20contribution%20from%20a%20Telangana-based%20infrastructure%20company%2C%20Megha%20Engineering%20and%20Infrastructure%20Limited%20(MEIL).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20total%2C%20BJP%20encashed%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%206%2C060.5%20crore%20between%20April%2012%2C%202019%20and%20January%2024%2C%202024%2C%20as%20revealed%20by%20the%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20following%20orders%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20total%20amount%20redeemed%20by%20the%20party%20since%20March%202018%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhow-much-money-did-the-bjp-really-get-from-electoral-bonds%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%208%2C251.8%20crore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20a%20significant%20margin%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20largest%20donor%20was%20Megha%20Engineering%2C%20based%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20which%20contributed%20Rs%20519%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20the%20firm%E2%80%99s%20total%20bond%20purchases%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20966%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20between%202019%20and%202023.%20The%20company%20now%20owns%20a%20major%20stake%20in%20the%20TV9%20network.%20Another%20MEIL%20company%20Western%20UP%20Power%20Transmission%20Company%20Limited%20gave%20an%20additional%20Rs%2080%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20second%20place%20is%20QwikSupply%2C%20which%20is%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20the%20Reliance%20Group%2C%20at%20Rs%20375%20crore.%20The%20second%20highest%20donor%20for%20BJP%20were%20companies%20linked%20to%20Kolkata-based%20industrialist%20M.K.%20Jalan.%20In%20total%2C%20Madanlal%20Limited%2C%20Keventers%20Foodpark%2C%20MKJ%20enterprises%20and%20Sasmal%20gave%20Rs%20339.42%20crore%20to%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20no%20matching%20records%20for%20bond%20numbers%20which%20amounted%20to%20Rs%20466.31%20crore%20encashed%20by%20BJP%20among%20the%20data%20revealed%20on%20March%2021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20numbers%20shared%20with%20EC%2C%20the%20BJP%20encashed%20Rs%201%2C505.4%20crores%20in%202019%2C%20when%20India%20went%20for%20general%20elections%20in%20April%20and%20May.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwho-were-the-top-buyers-of-electoral-bonds-paying%5C%22%3EWho%20Were%20the%20Top%20Buyers%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Paying%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20largest%20three%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20BJP%20were%20as%20follows%3A%20Madanlal%20Limited%20contributed%20Rs%20175.5%20crore%2C%20Keventer%20Foodpark%20Infra%20Limited%20contributed%20Rs%20144.5%20crore%2C%20and%20Megha%20Engineering%20contributed%20Rs%20125%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20both%20Keventer%20and%20Madanlal%20Limited%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20same%20group%2C%20the%20two%20Jalan%20companies%20issued%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20320%20crore%20in%20May%202019.%20Additionally%2C%20in%20October%20of%20the%20same%20year%2C%20another%20family-owned%20firm%2C%20MKJ%2C%20contributed%20an%20additional%20Rs%2014.42%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20redemption%20of%20bonds%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20experienced%20a%20significant%20drop%20to%20just%20Rs%2073.89%20crore%20in%202020.%20The%20top%20three%20donors%20for%20the%20BJP%20during%20that%20year%2C%20each%20contributing%20Rs%2010%20crore%2C%20were%20Apco%20Infratech%20Pvt%20Limited%2C%20Infina%20Finance%2C%20and%20an%20individual%20named%20Raju%20Kumar%20Sharma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20incoming%20funds%20saw%20a%20substantial%20increase%20to%20Rs%20372%20crore%20as%20political%20activities%20resumed%20to%20pre-pandemic%20levels.%20The%20top%20three%20redemptions%20by%20the%20BJP%20were%20from%20Future%20Gaming%2C%20a%20lottery%20group%2C%20at%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Haldia%20Energy%20at%20Rs%2035%20crore%2C%20and%20Megha%20Engineering%20at%20Rs%2033%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20highest%20amount%20of%20bonds%20were%20redeemed%20in%202022%20when%20assembly%20elections%20were%20held%20in%20the%20states%20of%20Goa%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%20According%20to%20the%20newly%20disclosed%20data%20%2C%20the%20BJP%20encashed%20Rs%201763.54%20crore%20in%202022%2C%20which%20was%20the%20highest%20amount%20for%20any%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20electoral%20bond%20donor%20in%202022%2C%20QwikSupply%2C%20contributed%20Rs%20325%20crore%20in%20two%20instalments%2C%20one%20in%20January%20and%20the%20other%20in%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20top%20donors%20for%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20in%202022%20were%20Vedanta%20(Rs%20176.5%20crore)%20and%20Megha%20Engineering%20(Rs%20129%20crore).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202023%2C%20Megha%20Engineering%20upped%20its%20donation%20to%20BJP%20to%20Rs%20297%20crore%2C%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20for%20that%20year.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%20Bharti%20Airtel%20at%20a%20distant%20second%20at%20Rs%2093%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Western%20UP%20Power%20Transmission%2C%20the%20MEIL%20group%20firm%2C%20at%20Rs%2080%20crore.%20It%20had%20been%20yet%20another%20bumper%20year%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20for%20BJP%20which%20redeemed%20Rs%201676.3%20crores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20this%20year%2C%20BJP%20encashed%20Rs%20202%20crore%2C%20out%20of%20which%20Bharati%20Airtel%20gave%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Kolkata-based%20Rungta%20and%20Sons%20at%20Rs%2050%20crore%20too.%20Torrent%20Power%20was%20its%20third%20highest%20donor%20at%20Rs%2025%20crore.%20It%20had%20already%20encashed%20Rs%20202%20crore%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20deemed%20the%20whole%20process%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711077535000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22084733%2FGJCLQayb0AA6lrb-e1711077496883.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmegha-engineering-qwiksupply-jalan-bjp-electoral-bond-top%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20total%2C%20BJP%20encashed%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%206060.5%20crore%20between%20April%2012%2C%202019%20and%20January%2024%2C%202024%2C%20reveals%20the%20newly%20released%20data.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmegha-engineering-qwiksupply-jalan-bjp-electoral-bond-top%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Jadeja%20went...'%3A%20CSK%20coach%20after%20Ruturaj%20replaces%20Dhoni%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711076921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108692787%2Cimgsize-164998.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fjadeja-went-into-csk-coach-stephen-fleming-after-ruturaj-gaikwad-replaces-ms-dhoni-as-captain%2Farticleshow%2F108692768.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20past%2C%20when%20MS%20Dhoni%20passed%20on%20captainc