(Pranab)%20said%20that%20he%20(Rahul)%20is%20yet%20to%20mature%20politically%20and%20he%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20seriously%20frequently%20absent.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20praise%20about%20Congress%2C%20but%20everything%20was%20ignored%20and%20Congress%20social%20media%20and%20some%20of%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20also%20had%20been%20speaking%20against%20...%20Congress%20social%20media%20had%20been%20viciously%20trolling%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mukherjee%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukherjee%20had%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20Congress%20saying%2C%20she%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20party.%26quot%3BA%20few%20days%20back%2C%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Jaipur%20Literature%20Festival%2C%20I%20made%20a%20statement%20in%20an%20interview%20and%20I%20was%20asked%20about%20my%20views%20about%20the%20Congress.%20I%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20I%20am%20a%20Congressperson%2C%20and%20Congress%20still%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20importance%20to%20play%20in%20national%20politics.%20But%20the%20Congress%20should%20look%20beyond%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Gandhi-Nehru%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmistha%20Mukherjee%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20should%20think%20about%20whom%20to%20project%20as%20its%20face%2C%20as%20the%20party%20had%20lost%20badly%20in%20the%20last%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20party's%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20from%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20arrived%20at%20Kejriwal's%20residence%20on%20Thursday%20to%20interrogate%20him%20regarding%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20During%20a%20search%20operation%20conducted%20at%20his%20residence%2C%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20amidst%20dramatic%20circumstances%2C%20as%20the%20AAP%20convener%20failed%20to%20obtain%20interim%20protection%20from%20arrest%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%20from%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20took%20him%20