%20eyes%20on%20Apple%20Inc.%2C%20unnerving%20investors%20with%20fears%20over%20fines%20and%20threatening%20its%20market%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%2016%20attorneys%20general%20are%20suing%20the%20iPhone%20maker%20for%20violating%20antitrust%20laws.%20And%20in%20Europe%2C%20the%20company%20is%20said%20to%20be%20facing%20probes%20about%20whether%20it's%20complying%20with%20the%20region's%20Digital%20Markets%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20the%20company%20slid%204.1%25%20Thursday%2C%20erasing%20about%20%24113%20billion%20in%20market%20value%20and%20taking%20their%20year-to-date%20loss%20back%20to%2011%25.%20Once%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20firm%20at%20more%20than%20%243%20trillion%2C%20Apple%20has%20underperformed%20both%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Apple%20is%20coming%20under%20regulatory%20scrutiny.%20The%20company%20and%20its%20peers%20have%20for%20years%20faced%20accusations%20of%20enriching%20themselves%20by%20suppressing%20competitors.%20But%20as%20Apple's%20products%20have%20grown%20ever-more%20popular%20and%20established%20themselves%20as%20part%20of%20daily%20life%20around%20the%20world%2C%20authorities%20have%20also%20become%20more%20combative%20and%20wary%20of%20its%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20suit%2C%20filed%20Thursday%20in%20New%20Jersey%20federal%20court%2C%20accuses%20Apple%20of%20blocking%20rivals%20from%20accessing%20hardware%20and%20software%20features%20on%20its%20popular%20devices.%20The%20potential%20investigations%20in%20Europe%2C%20which%20are%20also%20targeting%20some%20of%20Apple's%20rivals%2C%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20firm's%20new%20fees%2C%20terms%20and%20conditions%20for%20app%20store%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20comes%20a%20point%20in%20which%20the%20downpour%20of%20cases%20and%20scrutiny%20that%20comes%20with%20them%20become%20a%20real%20drag%20on%20how%20these%20companies%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bill%20Kovacic%2C%20an%20antitrust%20professor%20at%20George%20Washington%20University%20Law%20School.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20they%20win%2C%20in%20an%20important%20way%20they've%20lost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20fired%20back%20at%20the%20US%20lawsuit%20by%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20on%20the%20facts%20and%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%20It%20warned%20that%20the%20action%20would%20%26quot%3Bset%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%2C%20empowering%20government%20to%20take%20a%20heavy%20hand%20in%20designing%20people's%20technology%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bvigorously%20defend%20against%20it.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20potential%20European%20probes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Apple%20has%20used%20its%20power%20over%20app%20distribution%20on%20the%20iPhone%20to%20thwart%20innovations%20that%20would%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20consumers%20to%20switch%20phones.%20The%20company%20has%20refused%20to%20support%20cross-platform%20messaging%20apps%2C%20limited%20third-party%20digital%20wallets%20and%20non-Apple%20smartwatches%2C%20and%20blocked%20mobile%20cloud%20streaming%20services%2C%20according%20to%20the%20DOJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20highlights%20five%20examples%20of%20technologies%20in%20which%20it%20says%20Apple%20suppresses%20competition%3A%20super%20apps%2C%20cloud%20streaming%20game%20apps%2C%20messaging%20apps%2C%20smartwatches%20and%20digital%20wallets.%20The%20company%20recently%20added%20support%20for%20cloud-based%20gaming%20services%20and%20said%20it%20would%20add%20RCS%20cross-platform%20messaging%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Apple%2C%20we%20innovate%20every%20day%20to%20make%20technology%20people%20love%20-%20designing%20products%20that%20work%20seamlessly%20together%2C%20protect%20people's%20privacy%20and%20security%2C%20and%20create%20a%20magical%20experience%20for%20our%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThis%20lawsuit%20threatens%20who%20we%20are%20and%20the%20principles%20that%20set%20Apple%20products%20apart%20in%20fiercely%20competitive%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%20-%20which%20lays%20out%20a%20series%20of%20do's%20and%20don'ts%20for%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20tech%20platforms%20-%20allows%20European%20Commission%20to%20levy%20hefty%20penalties%20of%20as%20much%20as%2010%25%20of%20a%20company's%20total%20annual%20worldwide%20revenue%2C%20and%20up%20to%2020%25%20for%20firms%20who%20repeatedly%20flout%20the%20rules.%20After%20starting%20formal%20investigations%20into%20Apple%20-%20as%20well%20as%20Alphabet%20Inc.'s%20Google%20-%20regulators%20aim%20to%20wrap%20up%20their%20final%20decisions%20within%20a%20period%20of%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20fresh%20from%20its%201.8%20billion%20pounds%20(%242%20billion)%20European%20Union%20fine%20for%20blocking%20music%20streaming%20apps%20from%20informing%20users%20of%20cheaper%20deals%2C%20has%20been%20under%20heavy%20scrutiny%20since%20the%20DMA%20came%20into%20full%20effect%20on%20March%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711072320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2Fs59joum8_apple-generic-reuters-650_625x300_30_October_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-loses-113-billion-in-market-value-as-regulators-close-in-5287103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Regulators%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20Atlantic%20are%20training%20their%20eyes%20on%20Apple%20Inc.%2C%20unnerving%20investors%20with%20fears%20over%20fines%20and%20threatening%20its%20market%20dominance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-loses-113-billion-in-market-value-as-regulators-close-in-5287103%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22http