4-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManoj%20Bhargava%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20hiding%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20undeclared%20offshore%20bank%20accounts%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Sen.%20Ron%20Wyden%2C%20an%20Oregon%20Democrat%20and%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Senate%20Finance%20Committee%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finance.senate.gov%2Fchairmans-news%2Fwyden-launches-investigation-of-potential-ongoing-us-tax-evasion-at-swiss-bank-pictet-banks-deferred-prosecution-agreement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20on%20Thursday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he's%20launching%20an%20investigation%20into%20Geneva-based%20bank%20Pictet%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20committee%20probe%20into%20foreign%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finance.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Fredacted_wyden_letter_to_pictet.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20letter%20to%20Pictet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wyden%20accused%20the%20Swiss%20bank%20of%20conspiring%20to%20help%20ultra-high-net-worth%20Americans%20evade%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Wyden's%20letter%20alleges%20that%20one%20particular%20%26quot%3Bbillionaire%26quot%3B%20illegally%20hid%20at%20least%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20through%20Pictet%20over%20the%20course%20of%20his%2015-year%20relationship%20with%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20letter%20only%20identifies%20the%20billionaire%20as%20%26quot%3BPerson%201%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20investigation%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3BPerson%201%26quot%3B%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20referencing%20Bhargava%2C%20a%20US%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Bhargava%20did%20not%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F03%2F21%2Ffive-hour-energy-billionaire-named-in-senate-swiss-bank-tax-probe-source.h