0impossibility%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%20%26quot%3Bdefendants'%20ongoing%20diligent%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20attorneys%20wrote%20in%20the%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20once%20again%20railed%20against%20his%20massive%20civil%20fraud%20judgment%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F112134037818224958%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20Thursday%20to%20his%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20Truth%20Social%2C%20and%20insisted%20he%20did%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president%20said%20the%20judge%20who%20presided%20over%20his%20fraud%20trial%2C%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron%20of%20New%20York's%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20%26quot%3Bpicked%20a%20number%20out%20of%20THIN%20AIR%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwants%20me%20to%20bond%20it%2C%20which%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20bonding%20companies%20to%20do%20in%20such%20a%20high%20amount%2C%20before%20I%20can%20even%20Appeal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20CRAZY!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20fumed.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20sold%20assets%2C%20and%20then%20won%20the%20Appeal%2C%20the%20assets%20would%20be%20forever%20gone.%20Also%2C%20putting%20up%20money%20before%20an%20Appeal%20is%20VERY%20EXPENSIVE.%20When%20I%20win%20the%20Appeal%2C%20all%20of%20that%20money%20is%20gone%2C%20and%20I%20would%20have%20done%20nothing%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-new-york-attorney-general-civil-fraud-judgement-donations-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711050046000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fc70184af076d3cf927a8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-new-york-attorney-general-civil-fraud-judgement-donations-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20could%20land%20in%20legal%20ho