y%20laundering%20angle%20in%20the%20case%2C%20turned%20up%20at%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20house%20in%20the%20evening.%20After%20a%20search%20and%20questioning%20session%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20around%209%20pm%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20ED%20office%20in%20Delhi%20two%20hours%20later.%20He%20will%20remain%20in%20the%20ED%20lock-up%20tonight%20after%20a%20medical%20check-up%20from%20the%20RML%20hospital%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20from%20outside%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20official%20residence%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20not%20just%20a%20man%2C%20he%20is%20an%20idea.%20If%20you%20think%20arresting%20one%20Kejriwal%20can%20finish%20off%20the%20idea%2C%20you%20are%20wrong.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%2C%20was%20and%20will%20remain%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister.%20We%20have%20said%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%20he%20will%20run%20the%20government%20from%20jail%20if%20need%20be.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20convicted...%20No%20law%20stops%20him%20from%20doing%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20post-midnight%20press%20conference%2C%20AAP%20said%20it%20was%20called%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20Friday.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20the%20protest%20will%20take%20place%20outside%20the%20BJP%20headquarters.%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20stand%20with%20us%2C'%20said%20Ms%20Atishi%2C%20who%20is%20second%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20too%20place%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20skipped%20the%20ninth%20summons%20for%20questioning%20by%20the%20ED%20earlier%20on%20Thursday.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20refused%20to%20grant%20him%20protection%20from%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ED%20team%2C%20comprising%2012%20officials%20and%20led%20by%20Additional%20Director%20Kapil%20Raj%20--%20the%20officer%20who%20arrested%20former%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20January%20%E2%80%93%20had%20reached%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20residence%20with%20a%20search%20warrant.%20His%20and%20his%20wife's%20phones%20were%20confiscated%20and%20data%20was%20transferred%20from%20two%20tablets%20and%20a%20laptop%20at%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20ED%20officials%20carried%20out%20their%20questioning%20inside%20the%20residence%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20personnel%20as%20well%20as%20CRPF%20teams%20were%20deployed%20outside.%20Prohibitory%20orders%20were%20imposed%20in%20the%20area%20outside%20the%20residence%20and%20several%20AAP%20workers%2C%20who%20had%20gathered%20to%20protest%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20were%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fs65dfim8_arvind-kejriwal-arrest-aap-workers-detained_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EK%20Kavitha%20Link%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20chief%20minister's%20arrest%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20week%20after%20BRS%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20After%20her%20arrest%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20named%20as%20a%20conspirator%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-enforcement-directorate-wants-to-arrest-arvind-kejriwal-5284508%5C%22%3EExplained%3A%20Why%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Arrested%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20first%20summons%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20October%20last%20year%20and%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20appear%20on%20November%202%2C%20there%20has%20been%20intense%20speculation%20that%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20would%20be%20arrested%20by%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20put%20behind%20bars%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20in%20February%20last%20year%2C%20and%20AAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20scam%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20and%20the%20ED%2C%20which%20he%20claims%20is%20controlled%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20is%20out%20to%20arrest%20him.%20The%20AAP%20and%20many%20other%20opposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20misusing%20central%20agencies%20against%20their%20leaders.%20The%20harassment%20of%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20they%20have%20claimed%2C%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20on%20April%2019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-arvind-kejriwal-is-arrested-raghav-chadha-talks-of-big-conspiracy-5284810%5C%22%3EAs%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Is%20Arrested%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%20Talks%20Of%20%26quot%3BBig%20Conspiracy%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP's%20allies%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20including%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20also%20condemned%20the%20arrest.%20%26quot%3BTargeting%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Shri%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20this%20manner%20due%20to%20elections%20is%20completely%20wrong%20and%20unconstitutional.%20Lowering%20the%20level%20of%20politics%20in%20this%20manner%20suits%20neither%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20nor%20his%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20had%20declined%20to%20give%20protection%20from%20arrest%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20but%20had%20asked%20the%20ED%20to%20file%20a%20reply%20to%20his%20petition.%20Listing%20the%20matter%20for%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20April%2022%2C%20a%20Bench%20of%20Justices%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20and%20Manoj%20Jain%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20heard%20both%20sides%2C%20and%20we%20are%20not%20inclined%20at%20this%20stage%20(to%20grant%20protection).%20The%20respondent%20(ED)%20is%20at%20liberty%20to%20file%20a%20reply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Conspirator'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20note%20released%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20called%20the%20AAP%20chief%20a%20conspirator%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BED%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20Ms%20K%20Kavitha%20along%20with%20others%20conspired%20with%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20AAP%20including%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Manish%20Sisodia%20for%20getting%20favours%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Excise%20policy%20formulation%20and%20implementation.%20In%20exchange%20of%20these%20favours%2C%20she%20was%20involved%20in%20paying%20Rs%20100%20Crore%20to%20the%20leaders%20of%20AAP%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20note%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20acts%20of%20corruption%20and%20conspiracy%20in%20the%20formulation%20and%20implementation%20of%20Delhi%20Excise%20Policy%202021-22%2C%20a%20continuous%20stream%20of%20illegal%20funds%20in%20the%20form%20of%20kickback%2C%20from%20the%20wholesalers%20was%20generated%20for%20the%20AAP.%20Further%2C%20Smt%20K%20Kavitha%20and%20her%20associates%20were%20to%20recover%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20paid%20in%20advance%20to%20AAP%20and%20to%20further%20generate%20profits%2Fproceeds%20of%20crime%20from%20this%20entire%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Case%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20liquor%20policy%2C%20introduced%20in%20November%202021%2C%20the%20government%20withdrew%20from%20retail%20sale%20of%20liquor%20and%20allowed%20private%20licensees%20to%20run%20stores.%20In%20July%202022%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%20flagged%20gross%20violations%20in%20the%20policy%20and%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bundue%20benefits%26quot%3B%20to%20liquor%20licensees.%20The%20policy%20was%20scrapped%20in%20September%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20alleged%20that%20liquor%20companies%20were%20involved%20in%20framing%20the%20excise%20policy%2C%20which%20would%20have%20earned%20them%20a%2012%25%20profit.on%20the%20wholesale%20side.%20It%20said%20a%20liquor%20lobby%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Group%26quot%3B%20-%20of%20which%20Ms%20Kavitha%20was%20allegedly%20a%20member%20-%20had%20paid%20kickbacks%2C%20part%20of%20which%20were%20routed%20to%20public%20servants.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20alleged%20laundering%20of%20the%20kickbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20alleged%20scam%20were%20used%20by%20the%20AAP%20to%20fund%20its%20campaign%20for%20the%20Gujarat%20Assembly%20polls%20in%202022%2C%20in%20which%20it%20got%2012.91%25%20of%20the%20votes%20and%20established%20itself%20as%20a%20national%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711049160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fm7i2ee2_arvind-kejriwal-arrested-ani_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-liquor-policy-case-5284679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20seismic%20development%20in%20the%20national%20capital's%20politics%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-liquor-policy-case-5284679%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-liquor-policy-case-5284679%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-liquor-policy-case-5284679%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Will%20Replace%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3F%20Massive%20Leadership%20Crisis%20Facing%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20in%20the%20alleged%20excise%20policy%20scam%20has%20posed%20a%20leadership%20crisis%20in%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20with%20his%20wife%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20and%20cabinet%20ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20being%20talked%20about%20as%20a%20possible%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20before%20the%20AAP%20now%20is%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20worthy%20leader%20who%20can%20handle%20both%20the%20party%20and%20its%20government%20in%20Delhi%20in%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20absence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20indeed%20a%20big%20task%20for%20the%20AAP%20leadership%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20name%20that%20at%20least%20comes%20close%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20stature%20as%20the%20party's%20convener%20since%20its%20inception%20in%202012%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20three%20terms%20spanning%20nearly%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20urgency%20of%20the%20task%20becomes%20even%20more%20pressing%20as%20the%20AAP%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Assam%2C%20and%20Haryana%20where%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20to%20be%20a%20key%20campaigner%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20a%20former%20IRS%20officer%2C%20the%20names%20of%20AAP%20Ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20too%20are%20ding%20the%20rounds%20for%20the%20top%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20most%20number%20of%20portfolios%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20including%20education%2C%20finance%2C%20PWD%2C%20revenue%20and%20services%2C%20is%20considered%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20also%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20party%2C%20who%20has%20been%20defending%20the%20AAP%20government%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20and%20attacking%20the%20BJP%20in%20her%20press%20conferences%20and%20appearances%20on%20news%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20too%2C%20is%20also%20a%20prominent%20member%20of%20the%20Delhi%20cabinet%20with%20several%20important%20portfolios%2C%20including%20health%20and%20urban%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20a%20well%20known%20face%20of%20the%20party%2C%20often%20engaged%20in%20defending%20the%20it%20and%20its%20leaders%20and%20counter-attacking%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20on%20issues%20of%20governance%20and%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20the%20AAP%20launched%20a%20signature%20campaign%20%26quot%3BMain%20Bhi%20Kejriwal%20(I%20Am%20Also%20Kejriwal)'%2C%20asking%20people%20whether%20he%20should%20resign%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20or%20run%20the%20government%20from%20jail%20if%20he%20is%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20campaign%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%20met%20party%20MLAs%20and%20Delhi%20municipal%20corporation%20councilors%20for%20their%20feedback%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bharadwaj%20recently%20told%20reporters%20in%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20%26quot%3BNearly%2090%25%20of%20people%20in%20this%20exercise%20opined%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20the%20mandate%20of%20Delhi%20and%20has%20been%20elected.%20Hence%2C%20only%20he%20would%20run%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%20no%20matter%20from%20where.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leadership%20also%20has%20to%20find%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%C2%A0replacement%20to%20head%20the%20party%20that%20runs%20the%20governments%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20besides%20having%20MLAs%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Goa.%20The%20options%20are%20rather%20limited%20for%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%2C%20name%20of%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20and%20Atishi%20too%20are%20taking%20rounds%20as%20leaders%20who%20could%20hold%20the%20responsibility%20of%20new%20AAP%20national%20convener.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711048320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F8q354jt4_arvind-kejriwal-gujarat-ani-650_625x300_08_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-replace-arvind-kejriwal-massive-leadership-crisis-before-aap-after-arvind-kejriwal-arrested-5285043%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20has%20posed%20a%20leadership%20crisis%20in%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20cabinet%20ministers%20Atishi%20and%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20being%20talked%20about%20as%20a%20possible%20replacement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-replace-arvind-kejriwal-massive-leadership-crisis-before-aap-after-arvind-kejriwal-arrested-5285043%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-replace-arvind-kejriwal-massive-leadership-crisis-before-aap-after-arvind-kejriwal-arrested-5285043%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-will-replace-arvind-kejriwal-massive-leadership-crisis-before-aap-after-arvind-kejriwal-arrested-5285043%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Attorney%20General's%20Full%20Speech%20On%20Suit%20Against%20Apple%20For%20iPhone%20Monopoly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20on%20Thursday%20sued%20Apple%20for%20illegally%20maintaining%20a%20monopoly%20for%20its%20iPhone%20by%20stifling%20competition%20and%20imposing%20exorbitant%20costs%20on%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20was%20also%20brought%20by%20multiple%20US%20states%2C%20attacked%20the%20iPhone%20for%20raking%20in%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20by%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20consumers%20to%20switch%20away%20to%20cheaper%20smartphones%20and%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20joins%20Amazon%2C%20Google%20and%20Facebook-owner%20Meta%20which%20are%20also%20facing%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20US%20Attorney%20General%20Merrick%20Garland%20Said%C2%A0On%20Lawsuit%20Against%20Apple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20joined%20by%2015%20states%20and%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%20sue%20Apple%20in%20the%20U.S.%20District%20Count%20for%20the%20District%20of%20New%20Jersey%20for%20violating%20Section%202%20of%20the%20Sherman%20Antitrust%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20Apple%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20public%20companies%20in%20the%20world.%20Today%2C%20its%20net%20income%20exceeds%20the%20individual%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product%20of%20more%20than%20100%20countries.%20That%20is%20in%20large%20part%20due%20to%20the%20success%20of%20the%20iPhone%2C%20Apple's%20signature%20smartphone%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20iPhone%20sales%20have%20made%20up%20a%20majority%20of%20Apple's%20annual%20revenue.%20Today%2C%20Apple's%20share%20of%20the%20U.S.%20performance%20smartphone%20market%20exceeds%2070%25%2C%20and%20its%20share%20of%20the%20entire%20U.S.%20smartphone%20market%20exceeds%2065%25.%20Apple%20charges%20as%20much%20as%20nearly%20%241%2C600%20for%20an%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20our%20complaint%20alleges%2C%20Apple%20has%20maintained%20monopoly%20power%20in%20the%20smartphone%20market%20not%20simply%20by%20staying%20ahead%20of%20the%20competition%20on%20the%20merits%2C%20but%20by%20violating%20federal%20antitrust%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumers%20should%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20higher%20prices%20because%20companies%20break%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20allege%20that%20Apple%20has%20employed%20a%20strategy%20that%20relies%20on%20exclusionary%2C%20anticompetitive%20conduct%20that%20hurts%20both%20consumers%20and%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%2C%20that%20has%20meant%20fewer%20choices%3B%20higher%20prices%20and%20fees%3B%20lower%20quality%20smartphones%2C%20apps%2C%20and%20accessories%3B%20and%20less%20innovation%20from%20Apple%20and%20its%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20developers%2C%20that%20has%20meant%20being%20forced%20to%20play%20by%20rules%20that%20insulate%20Apple%20from%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20outlined%20in%20our%20complaint%2C%20we%20allege%20that%20Apple%20has%20consolidated%20its%20monopoly%20power%20not%20by%20making%20its%20own%20products%20better%20-%20but%20by%20making%20other%20products%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20carries%20out%20its%20exclusionary%2C%20anticompetitive%20conduct%20in%20two%20principal%20ways%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Apple%20imposes%20contractual%20restrictions%20and%20fees%20that%20limit%20the%20features%20and%20functionality%20that%20developers%20can%20offer%20iPhone%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20Apple%20selectively%20restricts%20access%20to%20the%20points%20of%20connection%20between%20third-party%20apps%20and%20the%20iPhone's%20operating%20system%2C%20degrading%20the%20functionality%20of%20non-Apple%20apps%20and%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20for%20most%20of%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Apple%20has%20collected%20a%20tax%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%2030%25%20commission%20on%20the%20price%20of%20any%20app%20downloaded%20from%20the%20App%20Store%20as%20well%20as%20on%20in-app%20purchases.%20Apple%20is%20able%20to%20command%20these%20fees%20from%20companies%20of%20all%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20also%20suppressed%20the%20emergence%20of%20programs%20like%20cloud%20streaming%20apps%20-%20including%20gaming%20apps%20-%20as%20well%20as%20super%20apps%20that%20could%20reduce%20user%20dependence%20on%20Apple's%20own%20operating%20system%20and%20expensive%20hardware.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20as%20any%20iPhone%20user%20who%20has%20ever%20seen%20a%20green%20text%20message%2C%20or%20received%20a%20tiny%2C%20grainy%20video%20can%20attest%20-%20Apple's%20anticompetitive%20conduct%20also%20includes%20making%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20iPhone%20users%20to%20message%20with%20users%20of%20non-Apple%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20this%20by%20diminishing%20the%20functionality%20of%20its%20own%20messaging%20app%20and%20by%20diminishing%20the%20functionality%20of%20third-party%20messaging%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20doing%20so%2C%20Apple%20knowingly%20and%20deliberately%20degrades%20quality%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20security%20for%20its%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20an%20iPhone%20user%20messages%20a%20non-iPhone%20user%20in%20Apple%20Messages%2C%20the%20text%20appears%20not%20only%20as%20a%20green%20bubble%2C%20but%20incorporates%20limited%20functionality%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20conversation%20is%20not%20encrypted%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVideos%20are%20pixelated%20and%20grainy%3B%20and%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20cannot%20edit%20messages%20or%20see%20typing%20indicators.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20iPhone%20users%20perceive%20rival%20smartphones%20as%20being%20lower%20quality%20because%20the%20experience%20of%20messaging%20friends%20and%20family%20who%20do%20not%20own%20iPhones%20is%20worse%20-%20even%20though%20Apple%20is%20the%20one%20responsible%20for%20breaking%20cross-platform%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20does%20so%20intentionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%202013%2C%20a%20senior%20executive%20at%20Apple%20explained%20that%20supporting%20cross-platform%20messaging%20in%20Apple%20Messages%2C%20%26quot%3Bwould%20simply%20serve%20to%20remove%20%5Ban%5D%20obstacle%20to%20iPhone%20families%20giving%20their%20kids%20Android%20phones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Apple's%20CEO%20was%20asked%20whether%20Apple%20would%20fix%20iPhone-to-Android%20messaging.%20The%20questioner%20added%3A%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20make%20it%20personal%20but%20I%20can't%20send%20my%20mom%20certain%20videos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20CEO%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BBuy%20your%20mom%20an%20iPhone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20selectively%20controlling%20app%20distribution%20and%20creation%2C%20we%20allege%20that%20Apple%20is%20violating%20the%20law%20by%20conditionally%20restricting%20developers'%20access%20to%20the%20interface%20needed%20to%20make%20an%20app%20functional%20on%20the%20Apple%20operating%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20product%20like%20a%20smartwatch%20or%20a%20digital%20wallet%20to%20be%20useful%20to%20an%20iPhone%20user%2C%20it%20must%20be%20able%20to%20communicate%20with%20the%20iPhone's%20operating%20system.%20But%20Apple%20creates%20barriers%20that%20make%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20and%20expensive%20for%20both%20users%20and%20developers%20to%20venture%20outside%20the%20Apple%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20smartwatches%2C%20Apple%20not%20only%20drives%20users%20to%20purchase%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20-%20which%20is%20only%20compatible%20with%20an%20iPhone%20-%20it%20also%20uses%20its%20technical%20and%20contractual%20controls%20to%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20someone%20with%20an%20iPhone%20to%20use%20a%20non-Apple%20smartwatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20digital%20wallets%2C%20Apple's%20exclusionary%20conduct%20goes%20a%20step%20further.%20Digital%20wallets%20allow%20users%20to%20store%20and%20use%20passes%20and%20credentials%20in%20a%20single%20app%20-%20including%20credit%20cards%2C%20personal%20identification%2C%20movie%20tickets%2C%20and%20car%20keys.%20Apple%20Wallet%20is%20Apple's%20proprietary%20digital%20wallet%20on%20the%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20actively%20encourages%20banks%2C%20merchants%2C%20and%20other%20parties%20to%20participate%20in%20Apple%20Wallet.%20But%20it%20simultaneously%20exerts%20its%20monopoly%20power%20to%20block%20these%20same%20partners%20from%20developing%20alternative%20payment%20products%20and%20services%20for%20iPhone%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Apple%20has%20blocked%20third-party%20developers%20from%20creating%20competing%20digital%20wallets%20on%20the%20iPhone%20that%20use%20what%20is%20known%20as%20tap-to-pay%20functionality.%20That%20is%20the%20function%20that%20makes%20a%20digital%20wallet%20-%20well%2C%20a%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Apple%20forces%20those%20who%20want%20to%20use%20the%20wallet%20function%20to%20share%20personal%20information%20with%20Apple%20-%20even%20if%20they%20would%20prefer%20to%20share%20that%20information%20solely%20with%20their%20bank%2C%20medical%20provider%2C%20or%20other%20trusted%20third%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20iPhone%20user%20puts%20a%20credit%20or%20debit%20card%20into%20Apple%20Wallet%2C%20Apple%20inserts%20itself%20in%20a%20process%20that%20could%20otherwise%20occur%20directly%20between%20the%20user%20and%20card%20issuer.%20This%20introduces%20an%20additional%20potential%20point%20of%20failure%20for%20the%20privacy%20and%20security%20of%20Apple%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20just%20one%20way%20in%20which%20Apple%20is%20willing%20to%20make%20the%20iPhone%20less%20secure%20and%20less%20private%20in%20order%20to%20maintain%20its%20monopoly%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20defines%20monopoly%20power%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20power%20to%20control%20prices%20or%20exclude%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20set%20out%20in%20our%20complaint%2C%20Apple%20has%20that%20power%20in%20the%20smartphone%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20having%20monopoly%20power%20does%20not%20itself%20violate%20the%20antitrust%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20does%20when%20a%20firm%20acquires%20or%20maintains%20monopoly%20power%20-%20not%20because%20it%20has%20a%20superior%20product%20or%20superior%20business%20acumen%20-%20but%20by%20engaging%20in%20exclusionary%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20set%20out%20in%20our%20complaint%2C%20Apple%20has%20maintained%20its%20power%20not%20because%20of%20its%20superiority%2C%20but%20because%20of%20its%20unlawful%20exclusionary%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonopolies%20like%20Apple's%20threaten%20the%20free%20and%20fair%20markets%20upon%20which%20our%20economy%20is%20based.%20They%20stifle%20innovation%3B%20they%20hurt%20producers%20and%20workers%3B%20and%20they%20increase%20costs%20for%20consumers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20left%20unchallenged%2C%20Apple%20will%20only%20continue%20to%20strengthen%20its%20smartphone%20monopoly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20law%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20will%20vigorously%20enforce%20antitrust%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnforcing%20the%20law%20protects%20consumers%20from%20higher%20prices%20and%20fewer%20choices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20legal%20ob