iness%2Finternational-business%2Freddit-the-self-anointed-front-page-of-the-internet-jumps-55-per-cent-in-wall-street-debut%2Famp_articleshow%2F108687075.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HC%20notice%20to%20Google%20India%20after%20techie%20loses%20access%20to%20Google%20account%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711046070000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108687141%2Cimgsize-386204.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fhc-notice-to-google-india-after-engineer-loses-access-gmail-google-drive-and-more-over-childhood-photo-labelled-porn%2Farticleshow%2F108687169.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShouldn't%20Have%20To%20Pay%20Higher%20Prices...%26quot%3B%3A%20US%20vs%20Apple%20Over%20iPhone%20Monopoly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20sued%20Apple%20on%20Thursday%20for%20illegally%20maintaining%20a%20monopoly%20for%20its%20iPhone%20by%20stifling%20competition%20and%20imposing%20exorbitant%20costs%20on%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20also%20brought%20by%20multiple%20US%20states%2C%20attacked%20the%20iPhone%20for%20raking%20in%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20by%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20consumers%20to%20switch%20away%20to%20cheaper%20smartphones%20and%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20anticipated%20case%20against%20Apple%20sees%20the%20company%20founded%20by%20Steve%20Jobs%20in%201976%20clash%20with%20Washington%20after%20largely%20escaping%20US%20government%20scrutiny%20for%20nearly%20a%20half%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20joins%20Amazon%2C%20Google%20and%20Facebook-owner%20Meta%20which%20are%20also%20facing%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20the%20lawsuit%20sent%20shares%20in%20Apple%20down%20by%20as%20much%20as%203.75%20percent%20on%20Wall%20Street%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20case%20is%20Apple's%20alleged%20exclusionary%20practices%20that%20set%20strict%20and%20at%20times%20opaque%20conditions%20on%20firms%20and%20developers%20seeking%20to%20reach%20the%20iPhone's%20136%20million%20US%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20these%20rules%20and%20decisions%20have%20been%20designed%20to%20force%20Apple%20users%20into%20staying%20in%20the%20Apple%20ecosystem%20and%20buying%20the%20company's%20more%20expensive%20hardware%2C%20the%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%20should%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20higher%20prices%20because%20companies%20violate%20the%20antitrust%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Attorney%20General%20Merrick%20Garland.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20left%20unchallenged%2C%20Apple%20will%20only%20continue%20to%20strengthen%20its%20smartphone%20monopoly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20fights%20back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20far-reaching%20case%20singled%20out%20practices%20that%20it%20said%20was%20making%20Apple%20richer%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20advancing%20innovation%20and%20technology%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Apple%20denied%20the%20merit%20of%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20on%20the%20facts%20and%20the%20law%2C%20and%20we%20will%20vigorously%20defend%20against%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20successful%2C%20the%20suit%20would%20%26quot%3Bset%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%2C%20empowering%20government%20to%20take%20a%20heavy%20hand%20in%20designing%20people's%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20for%20example%20accused%20Apple%20of%20squashing%20the%20creation%20of%20Super%20Apps%2C%20one-stop%20web%20portals%20that%20could%20exist%20on%20an%20iPhone%20and%20give%20consumers%20other%20ways%20to%20get%20services%2C%20such%20as%20music%2C%20photo%20or%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20big%20tech%20giants%20such%20as%20Meta%20have%20long%20dreamed%20of%20opening%20such%20super-apps%20on%20the%20iPhone%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20roughly%20half%20of%20the%20smartphone%20market%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accusations%20also%20target%20Apple's%20wallet%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20application%20allowed%20on%20the%20iPhone%20to%20access%20the%20technology%20to%20make%20tap%20payments%20in%20stores%2C%20forcing%20others%20to%20pay%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMessaging%20apps%20are%20under%20the%20microscope%20too%2C%20with%20prosecutors%20accusing%20Apple%20of%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20Apple%20users%20to%20interact%20easily%20with%20Android%20phone%20users%2C%20coercing%20them%20to%20buying%20the%20more%20expensive%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20broad%20case%20also%20mentions%20smartwatches%2C%20with%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20only%20being%20available%20through%20the%20iPhone%2C%20and%20competing%20smartwatches%20having%20very%20limited%20functionality%20on%20the%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20alleges%20that%20these%20nefarious%20practices%20go%20into%20other%20services%20such%20as%20web%20browsers%2C%20entertainment%20and%20even%20automotive%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%20Apple%20has%20invested%20heavily%20in%20promoting%20services%20as%20well%20as%20hardware%20as%20it%20seeks%20ways%20to%20make%20money%20beyond%20the%20iPhone%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20in%202007%20and%20changed%20the%20world%20of%20consumer%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20iPhone%20sales%20growth%20has%20been%20slowing%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20raising%20pressure%20on%20the%20company%20to%20find%20other%20sources%20of%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%20pointed%20out%20that%20Apple's%20profits%20exceed%20any%20other%20company%20in%20the%20Fortune%20500%20and%20that%20it%20exceeds%20the%20gross%20domestic%20product%20of%20more%20than%20100%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Apple%20saw%20global%20sales%20of%20%24383%20billion%20and%20net%20profit%20of%20%2497%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ's%20investigation%20of%20Apple%20began%20in%202019%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20largely%20won%20a%20US%20lawsuit%20from%20Fortnite-maker%20Epic%20Games%20that%20has%20been%20pursuing%20Apple%20in%20jurisdictions%20worldwide%20over%20the%20rules%20and%20fees%20it%20imposes%20on%20the%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20case%20brought%20by%20Spotify%2C%20the%20EU%20this%20month%20hit%20Apple%20with%20a%201.8-billion-euro%20(%241.9%20billion)%20fine%20for%20preventing%20European%20users%20from%20accessing%20information%20about%20alternative%2C%20cheaper%20music%20streaming%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711045620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Felfg8jmg_apple_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-sued-by-us-for-running-iphone-monopoly-in-wide-ranging-lawsuit-5284359%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20sued%20Apple%20on%20Thursday%20for%20illegally%20maintaining%20a%20monopoly%20for%20its%20iPhone%20by%20stifling%20competition%20and%20imposing%20exorbitant%20costs%20on%20consumers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-sued-by-us-for-running-iphone-monopoly-in-wide-ranging-lawsuit-5284359%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapple-sued-by-us-for-running-iphone-monopoly-in-wide-ranging-l