or-policy-case-live-updates-probe-agency-enforcement-directorate-at-arvind-kejriwals-house-with-search-warrant-5284002%5C%22%3EDelhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20and%20will%20remain%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi...%20there%20are%20no%20two%20ways%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20AAP's%20Atishi%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20his%20Number%202%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20it%20clear%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%20he%20will%20work%20from%20jail%20if%20need%20be.%20There%20is%20no%20law%20that%20stops%20him%20from%20doing%20so.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20convicted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-liquor-policy-case-5284679%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20first%20sitting%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20be%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20times.%20His%20continuing%20to%20work%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20from%20jail%20is%20likely%20to%20create%20a%20constitutional%20crisis%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20when%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20got%20arrested%20in%20the%20fodder%20scam%20case%2C%20he%20had%20handed%20over%20his%20charges%20to%20his%20wife%20Rabri%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20--%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20January%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20--%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20after%20he%20met%20the%20Governor%20and%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20is%20examining%20the%20ramifications%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20not%20resigning.%20Legal%20experts%20said%20the%20Centre%20may%20have%20to%20suspend%20or%20remove%20him%20from%20the%20post%20since%20he%20is%20a%20publi