%20(March%2021)%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20becoming%20the%20second%20sitting%20chief%20minister%20to%20be%20arrested%20in%20less%20than%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-arrest-likely-ed%5C%22%3E%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%2031%20in%20a%20case%20of%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20linked%20to%20a%20land%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EED%20officials%20arrived%20at%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsbi-submits-all-electoral-bond-details-including-unique-numbers-to-eci%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20website%20all%20details%20relating%20to%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20details%20include%20the%20unique%20numbers%20of%20purchasers%20and%20political%20parties%20which%20encashed%20these%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20released%20the%20information%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20which%20directed%20the%20disclosure%20of%20all%20electoral%20bond%20details%2C%20including%20the%20unique%20identification%20code%2C%20by%20March%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MLA%20Atishi%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20request%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20to%20quash%20his%20arrest%2C%20and%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20of%20a%20political%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20received%20news%20that%20ED%20has%20arrested%20Kejriwal.%20It%20was%20clear%20by%20the%20heavy%20police%20and%20para%20military%20forces%20presence%20that%20the%20ED%20would%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20today.%20His%20arrest%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20leader%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20scared%20of%20it%20is%20Kejriwal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20two%20years%20that%20this%20case%20has%20been%20going%20on%2C%20not%20a%20single%20rupee%20has%20been%20recovered%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI.%20There%20have%20been%20thousands%20of%20raids%20but%20not%20a%20single%20rupee%20has%20been%20recovered.%20His%20arrest%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20is%20a%20political%20conspiracy.%20If%20you%20think%20you%20finish%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20ideology%20by%20arresting%20him%2C%20you%20are%20wrong.%20Kejriwal%20was%2C%20is%20and%20will%20remain%20Delhi%20chief%20minister.%20If%20necessary%20he%20will%20run%20the%20government%20from%20jail.%20There%20is%20no%20law%20that%20prohibits%20this.%20There%20has%20been%20conviction%20against%20him.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20AAP%20leader%20Atishi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20received%20news%20that%20ED%20has%20arrested%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%E2%80%A6%20We%20have%20always%20said%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20will%20run%20the%20govt%20from%20jail.%20He%20will%20remain%20the%20CM%20of%20Delhi.%20We%20have%20filed%20a%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Our%20lawyers%20are%20reaching%20SC.%20We%20will%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXWQJ1D6ziR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXWQJ1D6ziR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1770839468490035318%3Fref_src%3Dtw