nister%20to%20be%20arrested.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20chief%20is%20the%20third%20senior%20leader%20from%20the%20party%20to%20be%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam%2C%20leaving%20question%20marks%20about%20the%20future%20of%20his%20party%2C%20which%20has%20insisted%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20run%20the%20government%20from%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20hours%20after%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20refused%20to%20grant%20him%20protection%20from%20arrest%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20He%20has%20skipped%20nine%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20last%20of%20which%20required%20his%20presence%20for%20questioning%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20same%20agency%20had%20arrested%20then%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20600-crore%20land%20scam%20on%20January%2031%2C%20the%20JMM%20leader%20had%20refused%20to%20sign%20the%20arrest%20memo%20until%20he%20tendered%20his%20resignation%20to%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20being%20taken%20away%20after%20being%20questioned%20for%20over%20six%20hours%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20had%20insisted%20on%20stopping%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20where%20he%20handed%20his%20resignation%20to%20Governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan.%20This%20ensured%20that%20he%20was%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%2C%20even%20if%20by%20a%20whisker%2C%20before%20his%20actual%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20other%20former%20chief%20ministers%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20been%20spent%20time%20behind%20bars%20include%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20late%20J%20Jayalalithaa%20of%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20of%20the%20TDP%20and%20Om%20Prakash%20Chautala%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%2