eight%3D%5C%22209%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20section%20related%20to%20display%20of%20the%20photographs%2C%20calendars%20etc.%20of%20national%20leaders%20and%20prominent%20personalities%20in%20the%20government%20offices%2Fpremises%2C%20etc.%20regarding%20the%20do%E2%80%99s%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20related%20to%20enforcement%20of%20MCC%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20mentioned%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20photographs%20and%20images%20of%20the%20political%20functionaries%2C%20who%20%5Bhave%20a%5D%20deep%20influence%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20electors%20and%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20still%20active%20in%20public%20life%20and%20may%20even%20be%20contesting%20the%20current%20general%20elections%2C%20should%20not%20be%20displayed%20in%20the%20government%20buildings%20and%20premises%20as%20that%20would%20have%20the%20effect%20of%20disturbing%20the%20level%20playing%20field%20vis-a-vis%20the%20political%20functionaries%20of%20other%20parties%20and%20candidates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20photographs%20of%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Chief%20Ministers%2C%20Ministers%20and%20other%20political%20functionaries%20should%20not%20be%20displayed%2C%20this%20instruction%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20applicable%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20images%20of%20national%20leaders%2C%20poets%2C%20and%20prominent%20historical%20personalities%20of%20the%20past%2C%20and%20the%20President%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Governors.%C2%A0%20In%20case%20of%20any%20doubt%20in%20this%20regard%20regarding%20removal%20of%20any%20photograph%20or%20images%2C%20the%20issue%20may%20be%20referred%20to%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20of%20the%20State%2F%20Union%20Territory%20concerned%20before%20taking%20action%20in%20the%20matter%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20other%20state%20government%20websites%20have%20now%20removed%20photographs%20of%20the%20chief%20ministers%20from%20their%20state%20webs