3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2065-year-old%20leader%20had%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20after%20Congress%20had%20denied%20him%20a%20ticket%20to%20contest%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Udhampur%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20of%20him%20rejoining%20the%20Congress%20have%20come%20amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-jammu-and-kashmir-minister-lal-singh-rejoins-congress-5277836%5C%22%3Especulations%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20will%20be%20fielded%20against%20Union%20minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20from%20Udhampur%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20April%2019.%20He%20also%20announced%20the%20merger%20of%20his%20outfit%2C%20Dogra%20Swabhiman%20Sangathan%20Party%20(DSSP)%2C%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-jammu-and-kashmir-minister-lal-singh-rejoins-congress-5277836%5C%22%3EGhulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20questioned%20the%20Congress%20for%20inducting%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20given%20his%20past%20conduct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKathua%20rally%20and%20exit%20from%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20in%20the%20BJP-PDP%20alliance%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20when%20he%2C%20along%20with%20his%20party%20colleague%20Chander%20Prakash%20Ganga%2C%20were%20forced%20to%20resign%20over%20their%20participation%20in%20a%20rally%20organised%20to%20support%20those%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Kathua%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20in%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20leaving%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%2C%20Singh%20launched%20his%20own%20outfit%2C%20DSSP%2C%20and%20contested%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Udhampur%20but%20was%20defeated%20by%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Jitendra%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20reading%20down%20of%20the%20Article%20370%20and%20reorganisation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20he%20became%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-minister-lal-singh-enforcement-directorate%5C%22%3Ea%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20policies%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20summoned%20Singh%20to%20the%20agency%E2%80%99s%20office.%20He%20was%20questioned%20for%20nearly%2011%20hours%2C%20which%20many%20saw%20as%20a%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-minister-lal-singh-enforcement-directorate%5C%22%3Evindictive%20action%20against%20him%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20is%20a%20two-time%20former%20member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Udhampur.%20He%20has%20been%20the%20health%20minister%20and%20forest%20minister%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20also%20represented%20Basohli%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20assembly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711027841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21160659%2FFNY-6m2aAAAxdvv.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fformer-jk-minister-lal-singh-rejoins-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202018%2C%20Singh%20participated%20in%20a%20rally%20in%20support%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Kathua%20gangrape%20case.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20he%20was%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20in%20the%20BJP-PDP%20alliance%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20position.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fformer-jk-minister-lal-singh-rejoins-congress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%3A%20K.%20Annamalai%2C%20Ex-Tel