rs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-screwed-up-how-us-lobbied-new-delhi-reverse-laptop-rules-2024-03-21%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2021).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-a-u-turn-union-govt-rolls-back-plans-to-license-laptop-computer-imports%5C%22%3Ehad%20imposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20import%20curbs%20on%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20computers%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20need%20to%20promote%20domestic%20manufacturing.%20However%2C%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-may-remove-the-requirement-for-mandatory-licence-to-import-laptops-pcs-tablets-report%5C%22%3Erolled%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20move%20that%20had%20rattled%20several%20companies%2C%20including%20US-based%20Apple%2C%20Dell%2C%20and%20HP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20had%20called%20the%20move%20as%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20protectionist%20and%20out%20of%20sync%20with%20the%20progress%20India%20has%20made%20in%20improving%20the%20investment%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20Korea%20had%20raised%20concerns%20over%20India%E2%80%99s%20move%20in%20a%20WTO%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2026%2C%202023%2C%20days%20after%20the%20import%20restriction%20policy%20was%20announced%2C%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20Katherine%20Tai%20met%20commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20USTR%20briefing%20paper%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters%2C%20said%20that%20although%20Tai%20%E2%80%9Craised%20concerns%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20policy%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnoted%E2%80%9D%20that%20stakeholders%20needed%20to%20be%20consulted%2C%20she%20privately%20told%20Goyal%20during%20the%20meeting%20that%20the%20US%20wanted%20India%20to%20%E2%80%9Crescind%20the%20requirement%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csurprise%E2%80%9D%20announcement%20%E2%80%9Cprompts%20US%20and%20other%20firms%20to%20think%20twice%20about%20doing%20business%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctalking%20points%E2%80%9D%20of%20her%20briefing%20paper%2C%20the%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20US%20diplomat%20for%20trade%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Travis%20Coberly%2C%20told%20his%20USTR%20colleagues%20that%20Indian%20officials%20had%20conceded%20the%20sudden%20rollout%20of%20the%20laptop%20licensing%20policy%20was%20a%20mistake%2C%20the%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20IT%20ministry%20%E2%80%9Cunderstands%20they%20(India)%20screwed%20up.%20They%20admitted%20as%20much.%20American%20companies%20here%20have%20been%20hammering%20them%20about%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20three%20Indian%20officials%2C%20including%20two%20from%20the%20commerce%20ministry%20who%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20since%20they%20were%20not%20authorised%20to%20comment%2C%20told%20Reuters%20that%20New%20Delhi%20did%20not%20reverse%20its%20policy%20under%20any%20US%20pressure.%20It%20reversed%20the%20decision%20as%20it%20realised%20local%20manufacturing%20of%20laptops%20and%20tablets%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20significant%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20import%20licensing%20move%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20policy%20that%20irked%20Washington.%20Several%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%2C%20including%20requiring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftech.hindustantimes.com%2Ftech%2Fnews%2Fmastercard-says-it-s-storing-india-payments-data-locally-in-face-of-new-rules-story-QyvLhyI76HY6O9E8obbuiI.html%5C%22%3EMastercard%20and%20Visa%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20store%20data%20locally%20and%20stringent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Ftrendspotting%2Fnew-india-e-commerce-rules-and-their-impact-explained%2Farticleshow%2F83914653.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ee-commerce%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20impacting%20Amazon%20among%20others%20firms%2C%20have%20also%20drawn%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emails%20reviewed%20by%20Reuters%20show%20HP%20told%20the%20USTR%20the%20laptop%20licensing%20%E2%80%9Cpolicy%20(and%20its%20goal)%E2%80%9D%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20problematic%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20our%20very%20wide%20Made%20in%20India%20portfolio%2C%20this%20would%20have%20significant%20impact%20on%20HP%20sales%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20head%20of%20global%20policy%20and%20strategy%2C%20Amy%20Burke%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711026035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06235340%2FIndia-and-US-n-A-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fgovts-move-to-roll-back-curbs-on-laptop-computer-imports-was-due-to-us-pressure-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20to%20impose%20import%20restriction%20rattled%20several%20companies%2C%20including%20US-based%20Apple%2C%20Dell%2C%20and%20HP.%20The%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20urged%20India%20to%20rescind%20the%20licensing%20requirement.%20However%2C%20some%20Indian%20officials%20said%20that%20the%20reversal%20was%20not%20due%20to%20US%20pressure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fgovts-move-to-roll-back-curbs-on-laptop-computer-imports-was-due-to-us-pressure-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20denies%20Navalny%20mother's%20case%20against%20prison%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711025916000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F16F4C%2Fproduction%2F_132982049_ee59e0c2fd813cb1e60a35ccc5164e2aeff3c8df0_3