ording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Ffir-against-union-minister-shobha-karandlaje-after-dmks-complaint-to-eci-101711017550327.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20booked%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%2023%20(3A)%2C%20125%20and%20123%20(3)%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20facing%20backlash%2C%20Karandlaje%20retracted%20her%20statement%20and%20issued%20an%20apology%2C%20clarifying%20that%20her%20remarks%20were%20misinterpreted%20and%20were%20intended%20to%20highlight%20specific%20incidents%2C%20not%20generalise%20against%20the%20Tamil%20community%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Fnews%2Fgot-the-viksit-bharat-message-on-whatsapp-sc-has-asked-govt-to-stop-it%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20my%20Tamil%20brothers%20and%20sisters%2C%20I%20wish%20to%20clarify%20that%20my%20words%20were%20meant%20to%20shine%20light%2C%20not%20cast%20shadows.%20Yet%20I%20see%20that%20my%20remarks%20brought%20pain%20to%20some%20%E2%80%93%20and%20for%20that%2C%20I%20apologise.%20My%20remarks%20were%20solely%20directed%20towards%20those%20trained%20in%20the%20Krishnagiri%20forest%2C%20linked%20to%20the%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%20blast.%20To%20anyone%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20affected%2C%20From%20the%20depths%20of%20my%20heart%2C%20I%20ask%20your%20forgiveness.%20Furthermore%2C%20I%20retract%20my%20previous%20comments%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20on%20Wednesday%20directed%20the%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Electoral%20officer%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Karandlaje%20for%20violating%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fec-karnataka-ceo-union-minister-shobha-karandlaje-mcc-9225198%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%