ocking%20is%20that%20though%20India%20generates%20three%20million%20metric%20tons%20of%20%E2%80%98used%20cooking%20oil%E2%80%99%2C%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20it%20goes%20toward%20biodiesel%20production.%20What%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20rest%3F%20This%20startup%20is%20encouraging%20food%20outlets%20to%20channel%20the%20%E2%80%9Cused%E2%80%9D%20oil%20to%20them%20to%20convert%20into%20biodiesel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20Tvaran%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%2030%20tonnes%20of%20used%20cooking%20oil%20per%20month%20have%20been%20collected%20from%20over%20250%20vendors%20in%20South%20India%20and%20recycled%20into%20biofuel.%20Kalyani%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Tvaran%2C%20the%20startup%20was%20introduced%20to%20The%20Chennai%20Angels%20(TCA)%2C%20from%20whom%20they%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20equity%20funding%20of%20Rs%203%20crore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuccess%20stories%20like%20these%20fulfil%20the%20intention%20with%20which%20Villgro%20and%20Cisco%20conceptualised%20Tvaran.%20Kalyani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20simply%20zoomed%20in%20on%20this%20particular%20strategy.%20The%20shared%20interest%20when%20it%20came%20to%20supporting%20women%20entrepreneurs%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20space%20helped%20us%20scale%20this%20idea%20into%20one%20that%20has%20impacted%20so%20many%20startups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tvaran%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20businesses%20and%20get%20mentored%20by%20industry%20experts%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomen-empowerment-3-1711018534-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETvaran%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20businesses%20and%20get%20mentored%20by%20industry%20experts%20.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20success%20of%20the%20first%20cohort%20enabled%20Villgro%20and%20Cisco%20to%20witness%20how%20market%20partnerships%20and%20support%20in%20implementing%20GTM%20strategies%20helped%20women-led%20businesses%2C%20as%20we%20advance%2C%20they%20say%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20fortify%20this%20cause.%20With%20the%20guiding%20belief%20that%20inventions%20are%20critical%20to%20driving%20change%2C%20the%20broader%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20these%20inventions%20get%20adopted%20while%20making%20communities%20resilient%20and%20improving%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202001%2C%20Villgro%20has%20backed%20387%20social%20enterprises%2C%20raising%20over%20Rs%204.7%20billion%20in%20investments.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20generated%208%2C175%20jobs%20and%20impacted%20over%2020.8%20million%20lives.%20Recognised%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20incubator%20in%202020%20by%20Invest%20India%20(DPIIT%2C%20GoI)%2C%20Villgro%20also%20won%20the%20DivHERsity%20awards%20in%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20picture%20credits%3A%20Villgro)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711022737000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345161%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tvaran%20%E2%80%94%20a%20joint%20initiative%20by%20Cisco%20(India%20Cash%20Grant%20Program)%20and%20Villgro%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20unique%20programme%20empowering%20women%20entrepreneurs%20who%20are%20driving%20innovative%20solutions%20in%20the%20climate%20action%20sector%20by%20providing%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance.%20Here%20are%20seven%20such%20startups.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Happiness%20Report%202024%3A%20India%20Ranks%20126th%20Out%20of%20143%20Nations%3B%20Behind%20Pakistan%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Palestine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FGuava1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%20was%20ranked%20126th%20out%20of%20143%20nations%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworldhappiness.report%2Fed%2F2024%2Fdifferences-in-life-satisfaction-among-older-adults-in-india%2F%5C%22%3EWorld%20Happiness%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%202024%2C%20a%20global%20happiness%20index%20which%20was%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20March%2020%20to%20mark%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20International%20Day%20of%20Happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20behind%20Pakistan%2C%20Libya%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Palestine%20and%20Niger%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%20by%20a%20partnership%20of%20Gallup%2C%20the%20Oxford%20Wellbeing%20Research%20Centre%2C%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Solutions%20Network%2C%20and%20the%20WHR%E2%80%99s%20Editorial%20Board%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EPTI%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-ranks-126th-out-of-143-nations-on-global-happiness-index-602622%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20seventh%20successive%20year%2C%20Finland%20topped%20the%20list%20of%20the%20happiest%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20top%20ten%20were%20Denmark%2C%20Iceland%2C%20Sweden%2C%20Israel%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Norway%2C%20Luxembourg%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20Australia.%20Afghanistan%20was%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPTI%20%3C%2Fem%3Equoted%20from%20the%20report%20that%20older%20age%20is%20associated%20with%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20in%20India%2C%20%E2%80%9Crefuting%20some%20claims%20that%20the%20positive%20association%20between%20age%20and%20life%20satisfaction%20only%20exists%20in%20high-income%20nations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlder%20men%20in%20India%20are%20more%20satisfied%20with%20life%20than%20older%20women%20on%20an%20average%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report%2C%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cbut%20when%20taking%20all%20other%20measures%20into%20account%2C%20older%20women%20report%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-google-query-id%3D%5C%22CNz7mo7whIUDFbaLZgIdaNwLRQ%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20revealed%20that%20older%20adults%20In%20India%20with%20secondary%20or%20higher%20education%20and%20those%20of%20higher%20social%20castes%20reported%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20compared%20to%20those%20without%20formal%20education%20and%20those%20from%20scheduled%20castes%20and%20scheduled%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20older%20population%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20worldwide%2C%20with%20140%20million%20Indians%20aged%2060%20and%20over%2C%20second%20only%20to%20its%20250%20million%20Chinese%20counterparts.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20average%20growth%20rate%20for%20Indians%20aged%2060%20and%20above%20is%20three%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20overall%20population%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20mentioned%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EPTI%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20older%20men%2C%20those%20in%20the%20higher%20age%20groups%2C%20currently%20married%2C%20and%20those%20who%20were%20educated%2C%20report%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20compared%20to%20their%20respective%20peers.%20Lower%20satisfaction%20with%20living%20arrangements%2C%20perceived%20discrimination%2C%20and%20poor%20self-rated%20health%20were%20important%20factors%20associated%20with%20low%20life%20satisfaction%20among%20older%20Indians.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711022433000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FGuava1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fworld-happiness-report-2024-india-ranks-126th-out-of-143-nations-behind-pakistan-iraq-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20seventh%20successive%20year%2C%20Finland%20topped%20the%20list%20of%20the%20happiest%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fworld-happiness-report-2024-india-ranks-126th-out-of-143-nations-behind-pakistan-iraq-palestine%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Macron's%20boxing%20photos%20show%20off%20his%20muscles%20-%20but%20he's%20not%20the%20first%20leader%20to%20try%20to%20flaunt%20his%20strength%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711022400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-emmanuel-macron-french-president_6496638.jpg%3F20240321105124%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Femmanuel-macrons-boxing-photos-show-off-his-muscles-but-hes-not-the-first-leader-to-try-to-flaunt-his-strength-13099061%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Emmanuel%20Macron's%20new%20boxing%20photos%20have%20impressed%20so%20many%20people%20online%20that%20he's%20got%20%26quot%3BRocky%26quo