C%20last%20four%20digits%20of%20the%20account%20number%2C%20prefix%2C%20bond%20number%2C%20denomination%2C%20pay%20branch%20code%20and%20pay%20teller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%20chairman%20submitted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprefix%20and%20the%20bond%20number%20is%20infact%20the%20alphanumeric%20number%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20affidavit%2C%20the%20chairman%20said%20that%20the%20complete%20bank%20account%20numbers%20and%20KYC%20details%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20are%20not%20being%20made%20public%20as%20it%20may%20compromise%20the%20security%20of%20the%20account.%20Similarly%2C%20KYC%20details%20of%20the%20purchasers%20are%20also%20not%20made%20public.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20not%20necessary%20for%20identifying%20the%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSBI%20has%20now%20disclosed%20all%20details%20and%20that%20no%20details%20(other%20than%20complete%20bank%20account%20numbers%20and%20KYC%20Details)%20have%20been%20withheld%20from%20disclosure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20has%20uploaded%20all%20the%20data%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20uploaded%20the%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20on%20its%20website%20as%20received%20from%20SBI%20on%20%E2%80%9Cas%20is%20where%20is%20basis%E2%80%9D.%20The%20data%20as%20received%20from%20SBI%20can%20be%20accessed%20at%20this%20url%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fcandidate-politicalparty%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20poll%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20SBI%20to%20disclose%20all%20electoral%20bond%20details%2C%20including%20the%20unique%20identification%20code%2C%20by%20March%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711017934000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21163904%2Fimage-1990.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsbi-submits-all-electoral-bond-details-including-unique-numbers-to-eci%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unique%20bond%20numbers%20would%20help%20match%20purchasers%20of%20the%20bonds%20with%20the%20political%20parties%20that%20redeemed%20those%20bonds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsbi-submits-all-electoral-bond-details-including-unique-numbers-to-eci%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20Is%20Your%20Governor%20Doing%3F'%3A%20SC%20Slams%20R.N.%20Ravi's%20Refusal%20to%20Re-Induct%20MLA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12172053%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-12-at-5.20.18-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20criticised%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%20R.N.%20Ravi%20for%20refusing%20to%20re-induct%20lawmaker%20K.%20Ponmudi%20as%20minister%20even%20after%20the%20suspension%20of%20his%20conviction%20by%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Ftn-governor-defying-supreme-court-seriously-concerned-about-his-conduct-supreme-court-slams-governor-rn-ravi-for-refusing-to-appoint-minister-253019%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20took%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20the%20delay%2C%20and%20asked%20Attorney%20General%20for%20India%2C%20R.%20Venkataramani%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20your%20governor%20doing%3F%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20conviction%20has%20been%20stayed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Governor%20says%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20swear%20him%20in!%20We%20will%20have%20to%20make%20some%20serious%20observations.%20Please%20tell%20your%20governor%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20take%20a%20serious%20view%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20asked%20as%20to%20how%20a%20governor%20can%20say%20%E2%80%93%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20stayed%20the%20MLA%E2%80%99s%20conviction%20%E2%80%93%20that%20%E2%80%9Chis%20reinduction%20as%20a%20Minister%20will%20be%20against%20Constitutional%20Morality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20consisting%20of%20Justice%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20was%20hearing%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20governor%20to%20accept%20the%20recommendation%20made%20by%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20to%20reappoint%20Ponmudi%20as%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20situation%20had%20constrained%20the%20court%20to%20express%20serious%20concern%20about%20the%20governor%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20say%20it%20out%20loud%20in%20court%20but%20you%20are%20now%20constraining%20us%20to%20say%20that%20aloud.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20way.%20He%20is%20defying%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20stressed%20that%20when%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stays%20a%20conviction%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Governor%20has%20no%20business%20to%20tell%20us%20that%20this%20does%20not%20wipe%20off%20the%20conviction%20and%20it%20is%20non-existent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20added%20that%20this%20means%20that%20those%20who%20have%20advised%20Governor%20Ravi%20have%20not%20done%20so%20%E2%80%9Ccorrectly%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20has%20sought%20time%20till%20tomorrow%2C%20March%2022%2C%20to%20respond.%20The%20court%20was%20stern%20in%20stressing%20that%20this%20deadline%20needs%20to%20be%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPast%20conflicts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20has%20had%20several%20run-ins%20with%20DMK-led%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20past.%20%3Cspan%3ERavi%20refused%20to%20read%20the%20c%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eustomary%20address%20prepared%20for%20him%20by%20the%20state%20government%20last%20month%2C%20and%20left%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20after%20abruptly%20ending%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20budget%20session%2C%20Ravi%20also%20omitted%20portions%20Ambedkar%2C%20Dravidian%20leaders%2C%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20of%20governance%20and%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20from%20his%20speech.%20This%20gesture%20was%20condemned%20by%20the%20Stalin-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20protested%20against%20Ravi%20as%20the%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHere%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20narrative%20has%20been%20created.%20Everything%20applicable%20for%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20say%20no.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20habit.%20So%20many%20theses%20have%20been%20written%20%E2%80%93%20all%20false%20and%20poor%20fiction.%20This%20must%20be%20broken.%20Truth%20must%20prevail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20state%20administration%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Condriya%20arasu%E2%80%9D%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20The%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711017922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12172053%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-12-at-5.20.18-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-rn-ravi-ponmudi-tamil-nadu-governor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20conviction%20has%20been%20stayed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Governor%20says%20he%20won't%20swear%20him%20in!%20We%20will%20have%20to%20make%20some%