ial%20responsibility%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSunlight%20is%20necessary%20for%20solar%20energy%2C%20and%20wind%20is%20needed%20for%20wind%20energy.%20However%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20lot%20of%20waste%20in%20towns%20and%20villages.%20By%20using%20waste%20for%20biogas%2C%20you%20get%20three%20benefits%20in%20one%20%E2%80%94%20fertiliser%2C%20useful%20gas%2C%20and%20efficient%20waste%20management.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20call%20it%20the%20king%20of%20renewable%20energy!%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%20is%20a%20testament%20effective%20to%20the%20power%20of%20perseverance%20and%20innovation%20in%20addressing%20pressing%20environmental%20issues.%20The%20company%20is%20not%20only%20contributing%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20more%20sustainable%20India%20but%20also%20setting%20an%20example%20for%20businesses%20worldwide%20to%20embrace%20eco-friendly%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kumar%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20simplest%20ways%20to%20express%20patriotism%20towards%20India%20is%20by%20segregating%20our%20waste.%20Adopt%20a%20two%20or%20three-bin%20system.%20Use%20one%20bin%20for%20electronic%20waste%20and%20hazardous%20materials%2C%20another%20for%20organic%20waste%20(coloured%20green)%2C%20and%20a%20third%20for%20dry%20waste%20(coloured%20blue).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20make%20sustainability%20a%20part%20of%20our%20daily%20thought%20process%20and%20actions%20for%20a%20better%20environment%20for%20our%20children%20and%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Greeneria)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710999169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345419%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founder%20of%20Greeneria%20R