Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20gathered%20mob%20had%20asked%20the%20women%20and%20the%20children%20of%20their%20community%20to%20stand%20before%20us.%20To%20avoid%20any%20hassles%20or%20misplaced%20blame%2C%20we%20had%20a%20force%20of%20female%20forest%20rangers%20on%20the%20sidelines%20too.%20There%20were%20even%20attempts%20to%20give%20this%20whole%20incident%20a%20communal%20angle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20dwellers%20went%20on%20to%20file%20petitions%20at%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20the%20State%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20High%20Court%20against%20the%20Forest%20Department.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20judgement%20was%20passed%20in%20our%20favour%20as%20we%20had%20all%20the%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20dated%2020%20June%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20writ%20petition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cencroachers%E2%80%9D%20and%20mentioned%20that%20the%20respondents%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20to%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rules%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20the%20help%20of%20forest%20guards%2C%20Jain%20was%20able%20to%20recover%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%