-the-case-3-min-1710763667-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Frest-the-case-3-min-1710763667-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345068%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShreya%20Sharma%20started%20Rest%20The%20Case%20in%202021.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ease%20of%20access%20when%20it%20came%20to%20finding%20legal%20help%20in%20the%20UK%20is%20what%20stayed%20with%20Shreya%20the%20most.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20these%20websites%20very%20interesting%20as%20I%20had%20not%20seen%20something%20like%20this%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20looked%20for%20similar%20websites%20in%20India%2C%20or%20a%20single%20website%20which%20would%20provide%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20to%20all%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315357%2Fmanilal-doctor-revolutionary-leader-freed-indentured-indian-labourers-in-fiji-mauritius%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20one.%20She%20then%20decided%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%20by%20building%20the%20solution%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20initial%20funding%20from%20her%20father%2C%20Shreya%20hired%20a%20few%20interns%20and%20built%20the%20website%20for%20Rest%20The%20Case%20after%20returning%20to%20Pune%2C%20Maharashtra.%20She%20ensured%20that%20every%20information%20posted%20on%20the%20website%20was%20written%20by%20a%20lawyer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20idea%20with%20Rest%20The%20Case%20is%20to%20provide%20vetted%20information%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20