ot%20give%20up%2C%20and%20after%20a%20five-year-long%20legal%20battle%2C%20the%20hotel%20was%20asked%20to%20refund%20the%20overpriced%20amount%20and%20pay%20Rs%202%2C500%20for%20harassment%20charges%20and%20Rs%203%2C000%20for%20other%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vijay%20Gopal%20(left)%20and%20Rohit%20Patel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVijay%20Gopal%20(left)%20and%20Rohit%20Patel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Vijay%20Gopal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Vijay%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20BookMyShow%20and%20the%20multiplex%20chain%20PVR%20for%20charging%20Rs%2080.12%20extra%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F180422%2Fpaytm-movie-tickets-internet-handling-fees-rbi-vijay-gopal-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternet%20handling%20fee%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20under%20Sections%2045%2C%2084%20and%2085%2